# UTF-8 encoding (mandatory)

All source files in this repo are **UTF-8** (no BOM).

## Never write corrupted characters

- Do **not** use `¯` (U+FFFD) or mojibake like `Ć§`, `Ć£`, `nĆ£o`, `VisĆ£o`.
- Use proper Unicode:
  - Em dash: `—` (titles, separators)
  - En dash: `–` (ranges: `500 – 999`)
  - Middle dot: `·` (inline separators)
  - Ellipsis: `…` (loading states: `A carregar…`)
  - Portuguese accents: `ć`, `ē`, `į`, `é`, `ķ`, `ó`, `ś`, `õ`, `ā`, `ź`, `ō`, `ą`, `Į`, `Ś`, etc.
  - Arrow: `?` (bidirectional links in comments)

## HTML

Every HTML file must include in `<head>`:

```html
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
```

## Before finishing edits

Run `npm run check:encoding` and fix any reported files.

## Saving files

- Line endings: LF (`\n`)
- Encoding: UTF-8
- Project defaults: `.editorconfig`, `.gitattributes`
